@mdakw576  
Don't forget about [Prophetic Prism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Prophetic Prism) or [Realmwright](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Realmwright) for "color fixing." Prisms are pretty amazing in limited, but this card is pretty good too.  

It's got it's place in the right constructed deck (I'd actually prefer this over [Farseek](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Farseek) in my green/white deck). Decent card. Deserves higher than a 2.6.

